Text:
If you like the album, don't buy it, artist don't earn money with cd's.
Just go to one of their shows, they are really amazing ;)

I've only just come across this band & i liked them straight away, very talented & would love to see them when next in the UK, Another band i REALLY love is Stooshe, they blow me away. Some great girl bands out there & i'm not talkin spice girlesque rubbish!
